Generic single-database configuration.

### Useful commands

´´´bash
# init alembic migration project 
alembic init alembic
´´´

´´´bash
# generate a migration based on models changes 
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"
´´´
[upgrade/downgrade](https://alembic.sqlalchemy.org/en/latest/tutorial.html#relative-migration-identifiers)
´´´bash
alembic upgrade head
´´´

